sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as Streamlit UI
    participant Pipe as LangChain Pipeline
    participant Claude as Claude API
    participant Tool as get_tracking_status

    User->>UI: Ask "Where is APG99999?"
    UI->>Pipe: question + chat history
    Pipe->>Pipe: Retrieve KB chunks and assemble prompt
    Pipe->>Claude: messages + retrieved context
    Claude-->>Pipe: tool_use(get_tracking_status, tracking_number=APG99999)
    Pipe->>Tool: Dispatch tool call
    Tool-->>Pipe: {status: "Held pending duties payment"}
    Pipe->>Claude: tool_result + same retrieved chunks
    Claude-->>Pipe: Final grounded answer
    Pipe-->>UI: Stream tokens
    UI-->>User: Show answer + feedback prompt

    alt Tracking number not found
        Tool-->>Pipe: {status: "Tracking number not found"}
        Pipe->>Claude: tool_result not_found
        Claude-->>Pipe: Ask user to verify tracking number
        Pipe-->>UI: Stream clarification response
    end